{"word":"Strangers","slug":"strangers","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Strangers</b> Mosaic law relating to:<br/> - Authorized bondservice of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=45'>Lev 25:45</a> <br/> - Usury of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=3'>Deu 15:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=20'>Deu 23:20</a> <br/> - Sale to, of flesh of animals that had died<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=21'>Deu 14:21</a> <br/> - Forbid their being made kings over Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=15'>Deu 17:15</a> <br/> - Forbid their eating the Passover<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=43'>Exo 12:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=48'>Exo 12:48</a> <br/> - Forbid their eating things offered in sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=33'>Exo 29:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=10'>Lev 22:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=12'>Lev 22:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=25'>Lev 22:25</a> <br/> - Forbid their blaspheming<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=16'>Lev 24:16</a> <br/> - Forbid their approaching the tabernacle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=51'>Num 1:51</a> <br/> - Forbid their eating blood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=10'>Lev 17:10</a> <br/> - Forbid injustice to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=49'>Exo 12:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=22'>Lev 24:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=14'>Num 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=16'>Deu 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=3'>Jer 22:3</a> <br/> - Forbid oppression of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=14'>Deu 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=17'>Deu 24:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=19'>Deu 27:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=3'>Jer 22:3</a> <br/> - Instances of oppression of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=22&verse=29'>Eze 22:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=5'>Mal 3:5</a> <br/> - Required to observe the Sabbath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=10'>Exo 20:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=12'>Exo 23:12</a> <br/> - Might offer oblations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=8'>Lev 17:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=22&verse=19'>Lev 22:19</a> <br/> - Were buried in separate burial places<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=7'>Mat 27:7</a> <br/> - Kindness to the poor of, required<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=38'>Lev 25:38</a> <br/> Love of, enjoined<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=10&verse=19'>Deu 10:19</a><br/> - Abhorrence of, forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=7'>Deu 23:7</a> <br/> - Marriage with, forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=25&verse=5'>Deu 25:5</a> <br/> - Hospitality to<br/> <a href='S:Hospitality'>Hospitality</a>; <a href='S:Alms'>Alms</a>; <a href='S:Heathen'>Heathen</a>; <a href='S:Proselyte'>Proselyte</a> "}]}